com.samsung.android.sdk.pen.document

Interface SpenPageDoc.HistoryListener

  • Enclosing class:
    SpenPageDoc

    public static interface SpenPageDoc.HistoryListener
    This listener interface provides callback methods for receiving history events.
    The interface receives notifications when a new history event is committed by SpenPageDoc.commitHistory(HistoryUpdateInfo)
    See Also:
    SpenPageDoc.setHistoryListener(HistoryListener)
